app_name: Groups Control Groups Photo and Video Editing Apps VITA Video Editor Maker
app_description: VITA is a simple easy video editing app with all features you need for videography! Start creating amazing videos with all the high quality features in VITA. Export videos in full HD quality. Speed up add slow motion with the video speed option. Add video transitions to make your videos look more cinematic. Make aesthetic videos with dreamy glitch glitter and bling effects. Apply filters to your videos for color grading. Select songs from the music library to enrich your videos. Create your own vlogs with quick and easy video templates. Use pre made fonts and animated texts customize with strokes shadows and colors. Collage and overlay videos with PIP to make clone videos.
